    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty ride and it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It runs super smoothly and has been really well-taken care of over the years. It\u2019s got plenty of life left in it and is looking for a new home where it\u2019ll be appreciated! It's been super reliable for me, and I think it's perfect for daily commutes or even a fun weekend road trip. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see this go to a great new owner!",
